Create a new project on Railway

Connect your GitHub repository

Add environment variable: GROQ_API_KEY

Railway automatically detects the Dockerfile and deploys

🧪 API Documentation
FastAPI provides interactive documentation at /docs:

Health Check: GET /health

Predict Price: POST /predict

POST /predict
{
  "text": "3 bedroom ranch with large garage in nice neighborhood"
}

{
  "price": 285000.0,
  "explanation": "This 3-bedroom ranch is valued at $285,000...",
  "missing_fields": ["LotFrontage", "Street"],
  "features": {
    "BedroomAbvGr": 3,
    "HouseStyle": "Ranch",
    "GarageCars": 2
  },
  "completeness": {
    "extracted_count": 3,
    "total_features": 11,
    "confidence": "low"
  }
}